What is the DOM?
An object representation of the html elements of a webpage

What is an event?
The way we users interact with the page

What is an event listener?
An event listener is a callback that you put on an elememt and when the event is triggered on that element, the callback is run.

Why would we convert a NodeList into an Array?
NodeList and arrays are similar, but Arrays offer methods like "forEach" that NodeList can't.

What is a component?
Reusable pieces of code that can be used to build elements sharing functionality and styling